<!--
  English (fallback) language pack for Pluma's i18n system.

  This file is source, not build output: it is parsed at *build time* by
  scripts/generate_embedded_languages.ps1, which emits src/ui/i18n_generated.cpp
  (a C++ byte table compiled into the binary). Nothing here is read at runtime.

  "en" is the mandatory fallback language: ui::i18n::Tr() falls back to this
  language's value when the active language is missing a key. Keep this file's
  key set the superset of every other language pack.
-->
